<title>百度“无限OCR”通过模拟人类遗忘机制一次性处理数十页文档</title>
<link>https://the-decoder.com/baidus-unlimited-ocr-processes-dozens-of-document-pages-in-one-pass-by-treating-memory-like-human-forgetting/</link>
